Package: nhanesR
Type: Package
Title: Download, Parse, and Analyze NHANES Data with Mortality Linkage
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Winsemius", email = "dwinsemius@comcast.net",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(credentials = "MD, MPH"))
Description: Provides tools for downloading and organizing National Health and
    Nutrition Examination Survey (NHANES) public-use data files and the NCHS
    Public-Use Linked Mortality Files (LMF). Supports structured local caching,
    codebook access, survey-aware merging, and preparation of survival analysis
    datasets using NHANES-NDI linked mortality data (follow-up through
    December 31, 2019).
    Developed with assistance from Claude Code (Anthropic).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
